## Memory layout

CLAUDE.md             — project guide
README.md             — user-facing summary
02-memory/
  decisions-log.md    — Phase 0.7 risk + subsequent decisions (Layermark
                        Cowork compatible format)
  doctrine/           — production doctrine (HIGH-RISK auto-loaded)
  category/<NN>.md    — category-specific patterns
  orchestrator-safety.md (if multi-agent)
  raw/ + wiki/ + schema/ (if knowledge base enabled — 3-layer KB)

## When you don't know what to read

- Generic question → CLAUDE.md → 02-memory/decisions-log.md
- Skill needed → .claude/skills/README.md (decision tree)
- Doctrine question → 02-memory/doctrine/<topic>.md (read on-demand only)
- Category-specific → 02-memory/category/<NN>-<slug>.md
- Past decision context → 02-memory/decisions-log.md

## Doctrine cap

Pocock smart-zone (~100K context). Read at most 5 doctrine files / 30KB
per request. If you need more, the question is too broad — narrow scope
first.

